data.description: This remodeled dream home comes complete with a refreshing pool and falls within the Martin High School zoning. Enter the front door to an elegant living room featuring coffered ceilings and a floor-to-ceiling brick fireplace. A flex space with a vaulted ceiling overlooks the pool and includes a wet bar. The kitchen boasts quartz counters, a custom vent hood, SS appliances, and a coffee bar. Head into the owner's suite with a walk-in closet, double sinks, a walk-in glass shower, and a separate tub. Front dining currently used as an office. Upstairs are 3 ample bedrooms, each offering sizable closets. Outside you'll find a gunite pool, a covered patio, and a deck complete with a built-in grill. An electric gated driveway and privacy fence for added privacy. The garage has been finished with epoxy floors, built-in cabinets, and a mini-split unit that provides both heating and cooling. This is a remarkable opportunity to own a gem just moments away from Lake Arlington.
